metadata.description:
This is an official, EraldMWhay created & approved, Eternal Pre-Sales Allowlist Ticket, the first ever to be minted.

Congratulations for obtaining this precious artifact, as long as you hold on to it, you will be part of the Pre-Sales Allowlist for all my future Foundation Drops.
